{
  "version": 1,
  "notes": [
    "Positive terms count gratitude, politeness, approval, and satisfaction signals in direct user messages.",
    "Matches are review leads, not proof of happiness. For example, please/пожалуйста can be politeness rather than satisfaction.",
    "A trailing * means a Unicode word-stem match, useful for Russian morphology and slang variants."
